<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0165 </DOCNO><TEXT>The authors examine an approach to preparing rational layouts for cuttingsheet metal and using scrap, involving the use of a computer. The benefitsof using a computerized approach are discussed. The layout of sheet metalfor cutting a set of standard trays is shown. The flexible, hybrid methodfor preparing optimum layouts for sheet metal cutting has helped thechemical equipment plants to further economize materials and increasethe coefficient of metal utilization, according to the authors.</TEXT></DOC>